      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S represents a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the 3.8L M97 flat-six engine mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing exceptional damping control and chassis composure through high-load cornering. Mechanically sound with documented service history, the engine exhibits strong compression and a clean bill of health regarding bore scoring concerns. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight, offering the visceral feedback and communicative steering rack synonymous with the 911 legacy. An excellent entry point for the serious driver.",
